  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a mysterious underground laboratory, dangerous creatures have escaped. The road to the surface is blocked by many obstacles, but top scientists never complain about the environment. The organs and genes of unknown creatures can be your power. Make good use of them and create yourself a path of flesh and blood. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/369f4429a08d97dc048dbb5dfd491bce.webp?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/b10819ce0bafbb97c3e99a5add9857d8.poster.avif?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/b10819ce0bafbb97c3e99a5add9857d8.webm?t=1747638427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/b10819ce0bafbb97c3e99a5add9857d8.mp4?t=1747638427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use simple programming logic to build organ links. The skill building process is highly visualized and can be easily debugged.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/e7efa015e5aec5499075d4838a5cdece.webp?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/5bea572a7cb1f88d3844b0d3f30b520c.poster.avif?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/5bea572a7cb1f88d3844b0d3f30b520c.webm?t=1747638427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/5bea572a7cb1f88d3844b0d3f30b520c.mp4?t=1747638427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The game includes hundreds of organs with different functions. Each organ can also be mutated to obtain additional affixes which can further generate more unpredictable changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/f8a2edeaf32384814f591a7300dc5453.webp?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=52 /></span>The difficulty of the game can be automatically adjusted to the progress of the game. After completing the main acts, there are still more difficult challenges, more modes and content to explore.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a mysterious underground laboratory, dangerous creatures have escaped. The road to the surface is blocked by many obstacles, but top scientists never complain about the environment. The organs and genes of unknown creatures can be your power. Make good use of them and create yourself a path of flesh and blood. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/369f4429a08d97dc048dbb5dfd491bce.webp?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/b10819ce0bafbb97c3e99a5add9857d8.poster.avif?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/b10819ce0bafbb97c3e99a5add9857d8.webm?t=1747638427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/b10819ce0bafbb97c3e99a5add9857d8.mp4?t=1747638427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use simple programming logic to build organ links. The skill building process is highly visualized and can be easily debugged.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/e7efa015e5aec5499075d4838a5cdece.webp?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/5bea572a7cb1f88d3844b0d3f30b520c.poster.avif?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/5bea572a7cb1f88d3844b0d3f30b520c.webm?t=1747638427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/5bea572a7cb1f88d3844b0d3f30b520c.mp4?t=1747638427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The game includes hundreds of organs with different functions. Each organ can also be mutated to obtain additional affixes which can further generate more unpredictable changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177970/extras/f8a2edeaf32384814f591a7300dc5453.webp?t=1747638427\" width=620 height=52 /></span>The difficulty of the game can be automatically adjusted to the progress of the game. After completing the main acts, there are still more difficult challenges, more modes and content to explore.</p>",
